About FAB

FAB believes that young people can be the solution to the new world problems they face. Our vision is to strengthen the policies that allow young people to realize their full potential and advocate for and support young people to access opportunities that enable them to act. FAB is founded by young people, but engages with experienced seniors and emerging leaders to help amplify voices to encourage meaningful change and contribute to the realization of the Sustainable Development Agenda 2030. There are women, minority, urban, rural, economically poor, and differently abled youth who define basic needs differently, so there is diversity in our membership, from the United Kingdom to the United States of America to Nigeria, Africa.
